<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>The person is holding a large square.</li>
      <li>There’s a playground in the background.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>How did the person make the large square?</li>
      <li>How long is each side of the square?</li>
      <li>How many squares would it take to tile the playground?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


